      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金价格因交易商消化零售数据和利率前景而波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/gold-xauusd-holds-decline-as-fed-s-rate-cut-trajectory-remains-unclear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员们消化美国零售支出数据，黄金价格出现波动，该数据凸显了世界最大经济体的实力，同时考虑到美联储下个月预期降息的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/gold-xauusd-holds-decline-as-fed-s-rate-cut-trajectory-remains-unclear</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 00:51:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗紧张局势和美国零售销售强劲推动油价止跌两日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对伊朗可能袭击以色列的担忧和美国强劲的经济数据掩盖了持续的需求担忧，油价在连续两天下跌后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 23:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据显示美国经济保持强劲，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asian-stocks-to-open-weaker-cpi-calms-wall-street-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于零售支出和劳动力市场数据凸显出全球最大经济体的实力，股市上涨，债市下跌，缓解了人们对美联储可能面临经济进一步放缓风险的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asian-stocks-to-open-weaker-cpi-calms-wall-street-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 22:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
